These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 8

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: collecting, card-games, photography, filmmaking
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: skiing, basketball, water-polo, swimming
1. the person who's hobby is photography is between the person who's sport is water-polo and the person who's sport is basketball##2
2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left or right of the person who's sport is water-polo##3
3. the person who's sport is water-polo is not to the left of the person who's sport is water-polo##8
4. the person who's sport is basketball is not the person who's hobby is photography##6
5. the person who's hobby is photography is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is collecting##5
6. the person who's hobby is collecting is on the right of the person who's sport is skiing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1     |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Hobby   | filmmaking  | collecting | photography | card-games  |
| Sport   | skiing | water-polo   | swimming  | basketball |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-2::.
There 4 different types of food: broccoli, orange, avocado, peas
The people have 4 different jobs:  librarian, chef, accountant, electrician
1. the electrician is not to the left of the electrician##8
2. the person eating broccoli is somewhere to the right of the person eating peas##5
3. the person eating broccoli is the chef##1
4. the person eating peas is between the person eating broccoli and the person eating orange##2
5. the person eating orange is somewhere between the person eating avocado and the librarian##7
6. the accountant is somewhere to the left of the person eating orange##5
7. the librarian is not to the left of the librarian##8

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |        2        |    3     |     4      |
| Food   | avocado | orange          | peas | broccoli     |
| Job    | accountant      | electrician | librarian | chef |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-3::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, social-worker, analyst, videographer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, martial-arts, animation, documentary
1. the person watching crime movies is not to the left of the analyst##8
2. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the far left##1
3. the social-worker is on the right of the architect##1
4. the social-worker is in an even position##4
5. the videographer is on the far left or far right##3
6. the architect is somewhere to the left of the person watching documentary movies##5
7. the videographer is the person watching animation movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |     3     |     4     |
| Job           | architect | social-worker | analyst     | videographer |
| Movie-Genre   | martial-arts    | documentary   | crime | animation    |

