.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-4::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, techno, country, pop
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: rowing, rugby, tennis, basketball
1. the person who's sport is rugby is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
2. the person who's sport is rowing is not to the left of the person who's sport is rugby##8
3. the person who's sport is tennis is on the right of the fan of techno##1
4. the fan of pop is not to the right of the person who's sport is tennis##8
5. the fan of punk is the person who's sport is rowing##1
6. the fan of punk is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
7. the fan of country is somewhere to the left of the fan of pop##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |   3    |    4     |
| Music-Genre   | country   | techno         | pop   | punk    |
| Sport         | rugby | basketball | tennis | rowing |

