.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-5::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, mystery, superhero, adventure
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: baseball, parkour, surfing, skateboarding
1. the person watching adventure movies is somewhere between the person watching disaster movies and the person watching mystery movies##7
2. the person watching superhero movies is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is surfing##5
3. the person watching adventure movies is somewhere between the person watching superhero movies and the person watching disaster movies##7
4. the person watching superhero movies is not to the left of the person who's sport is skateboarding##8
5. the person who's sport is skateboarding is somewhere between the person watching mystery movies and the person who's sport is parkour##7
6. the person who's sport is parkour is somewhere to the right of the person watching adventure movies##5
7. the person who's sport is parkour is not to the left of the person watching disaster movies##8
8. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the person watching adventure movies##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |     3      |    4    |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery   | superhero | adventure | disaster    |
| Sport         | baseball | skateboarding   | surfing   | parkour |

