2. the fan of folk is somewhere to the left of the person eating banana##5
3. the person eating artichoke is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
4. the fan of punk is on the left or right of the fan of hip-hop##3
5. the person eating banana is somewhere to the left of the person eating grapefruit##5
6. the person eating strawberry is not to the left of the fan of folk##8
7. the person eating strawberry is the fan of folk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |   3   |    4    |
| Food          | strawberry | banana | grapefruit  | artichoke |
| Music-Genre   | folk   | reggae         | hip-hop | punk |

