.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, tea, milk, soy-milk
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: snowboarding, ice-hockey, soccer, surfing
1. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is not to the left of the person drinking tea##8
2. the person who's sport is surfing is somewhere between the person drinking soy-milk and the person who's sport is soccer##7
3. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere to the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##5
4. the person who's sport is surfing is not to the left of the person who's sport is snowboarding##8
5. the person who's sport is surfing is not to the left of the person drinking tea##8
6. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left or right of the person drinking milk##3
7. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
8. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1     |   2    |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage   | tea      | milk | hot-chocolate | soy-milk   |
| Sport      | snowboarding | soccer | surfing  | ice-hockey |

