.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-9::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, rock, gospel, jazz
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, scooter, van, motorbike
1. the fan of reggae is between the fan of jazz and the person driving the tram##2
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the far left##1
3. the person driving the motorbike is on the left or right of the fan of reggae##3
4. the fan of rock is somewhere to the right of the person driving the tram##5
5. the person driving the scooter is the person driving the scooter##1
6. the fan of gospel is not the person driving the van##6
7. the fan of jazz is not to the right of the fan of gospel##8
8. the person driving the tram is not to the left of the person driving the scooter##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |     2     |   3   |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | jazz   | reggae | gospel | rock |
| Transport     | motorbike | scooter       | tram  | van    |

