.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-12::.
There 4 different types of food: cabbage, peach, lettuce, garlic
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, gardening, traveling, photography
1. the person eating lettuce is not to the right of the person who's hobby is photography##8
2. the person who's hobby is chess is not to the right of the person eating peach##8
3. the person who's hobby is gardening is somewhere to the right of the person eating garlic##5
4. the person who's hobby is chess is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person eating lettuce is between the person who's hobby is photography and the person who's hobby is traveling##2
6. the person eating peach is on the far left##1
7. the person eating lettuce is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is photography##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |    4    |
| Food    | peach        | garlic | lettuce      | cabbage    |
| Hobby   | chess | traveling   | gardening | photography |

