.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-13::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, tea, iced-tea, sprite
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: cricket, snowboarding, cycling, basketball
1. the person who's sport is basketball is not to the right of the person who's sport is cricket##8
2. the person who's sport is basketball is not to the right of the person drinking milk##8
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left of the person drinking tea##1
4. the person drinking milk is on the far left or far right##3
5. the person drinking sprite is on the far left or far right##3
6. the person who's sport is cricket is somewhere between the person who's sport is cycling and the person drinking tea##7
7. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
8. the person drinking sprite is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1     |       2       |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | sprite | tea         | iced-tea    | milk       |
| Sport      | snowboarding | basketball | cricket | cycling |

