3. the person who's hobby is video-games is somewhere to the right of the person drinking iced-tea##5
4. the person drinking lemonade is between the person drinking iced-tea and the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##2
5. the person drinking water is on the far left##1
6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the person who's hobby is chess and the person who's hobby is video-games##2

.:: Answer ::.
