 1. the person watching sports movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching satire movies##5
 2. the person eating spinach is not to the left of the person eating eggplant##8
 3. the person eating cabbage is the person watching satire movies##1
 4. the person watching satire movies is not to the right of the person watching musical movies##8
 5. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person eating mango##1
 6. the person watching musical movies is somewhere to the right of the person eating eggplant##5
 7. the person watching musical movies is on the far left or far right##3
 8. the person eating cabbage is not to the right of the person watching satire movies##8
 9. the person watching musical movies is not to the left of the person eating cabbage##8
10. the person eating mango is not to the left of the person watching mystery movies##8

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2      |     3      |    4     |
| Food          | mango    | eggplant | cabbage | spinach |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery | sports  | satire     | musical    |

