.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-18::.
There 4 different types of food: pumpkin, broccoli, potato, onion
The people have 4 different hobbies: cooking, skydiving, board-games, fishing
1. the person eating potato is the person who's hobby is cooking##1
2. the person eating potato is not to the left of the person who's hobby is skydiving##8
3. the person who's hobby is skydiving is the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
4. the person who's hobby is fishing is the person eating onion##1
5. the person eating onion is on the left of the person eating broccoli##1
6. the person eating broccoli is between the person who's hobby is skydiving and the person eating onion##2
7. the person eating potato is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
