.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-19::.
4 different pets are kept: rat, turtle, lizard, ferret
The people use 4 different means of transport: motorbike, skateboard, taxi, helicopter
1. the owner of the ferret is not the person driving the taxi##6
2. the person driving the taxi is not to the right of the owner of the lizard##8
3. the owner of the turtle is somewhere between the owner of the lizard and the owner of the ferret##7
4. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere to the right of the owner of the rat##5
5. the person driving the skateboard is somewhere to the left of the person driving the helicopter##5
6. the person driving the motorbike is not to the right of the person driving the skateboard##8
7. the owner of the turtle is not to the left of the person driving the helicopter##8

.:: Answer ::.
|             |  1   |   2   |   3   |    4    |
| Pet         | rat  | ferret | turtle  | lizard  |
| Transport   | motorbike | skateboard   | helicopter | taxi |

