.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-8-20::.
4 different pets are kept: dog, mouse, snake, rat
The people use 4 different means of transport: taxi, tram, scooter, trike
1. the person driving the tram is not the owner of the dog##6
2. the person driving the scooter is on the right of the person driving the trike##1
3. the owner of the rat is not to the left of the person driving the trike##8
4. the owner of the snake is the person driving the taxi##1
5. the owner of the rat is somewhere between the person driving the tram and the person driving the taxi##7
6. the owner of the rat is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
7. the person driving the scooter is between the person driving the trike and the owner of the snake##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2     |     3      |    4    |
| Pet         | mouse    | rat | dog | snake |
| Transport   | tram | trike      | scooter     | taxi     |

 